  "prompt": "Which is a good solar panel installation provider near Twain Harte, California CA?",
  "response": "While I can't provide real-time information or specific company recommendations, I can suggest some general strategies for finding a good solar panel installation provider near Twain Harte, California:\n\n1. **Online Research**: Websites like EnergySage, SolarReviews, and Yelp can provide customer reviews and ratings for solar installation companies in your area.\n\n2. **Local Companies**: Look for local businesses that specialize in solar panel installation. They may have knowledge of local building codes and incentives.\n\n3. **Consultation Services**: Reach out to multiple providers for consultations. This can give you a sense of their customer service, pricing, and the solutions they offer.\n\n4. **Check Credentials**: Ensure the company is licensed and insured. Many reputable solar companies are also affiliated with organizations like the Solar Energy Industries Association (SEIA).\n\n5. **Recommendations**: Ask friends, family, or neighbors who have installed solar panels for their recommendations.\n\n6. **Quotes and Comparison**: Get multiple quotes to compare pricing, services included, and warranties offered.\n\n7. **Look for Incentives**: Some companies may offer financing options or be able to help you navigate state and federal tax incentives for solar energy.\n\nOnce you gather this information, you should be in a better position to choose a reliable solar panel installation provider.",
